{"tid":1764170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：催淚煙、汽油彈及燒雜物釋出的有害物質均對健康有影響","createTime":"2019-12-01T02:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T13:29:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3b03619d651d2ffefb48f72603f602587be145b5","tid":1764170,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"反修例示威衝突持續近半年，警方施放約1萬枚催淚彈。食物及衛生局長陳肇始今日（30日）見記者時表示，醫管局接獲2600多宗因反修例事件求醫或輕傷的個案，包括吸入催淚煙的人。陳肇始強調，求診者接觸催淚煙後的反應都是短暫，全部人均已出院。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始指出，政府從未間斷與醫學專家及科學家評估催淚煙對市民健康風險的影響，據專家評估，催淚煙、汽油彈及燒雜物釋出的有害物質均對健康有影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191130/s00001/1575100069646/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191130%2Fs00001%2F1575100069646%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=848e0a8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191130%2Fs00001%2F1575100069646%2F&h=2d132d1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191130/s00001/1575100069646/</a>"},{"pid":"955c44d76cca5928ea2574523307a14036c4778b","tid":1764170,"uid":36158,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"呢條臭閪個閪真係好臭"},{"pid":"919477021e0ce48eb3083a5964c64e2c9f42f0e3","tid":1764170,"uid":199227,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"各打50？<br />\n屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"0641c7c9e9eb368771a55ce64aa731000e471cdf","tid":1764170,"uid":36287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:11:12.000Z","msg":"問你點影響 幾有影響 <br />\n你個垃圾護士仔答我<br />\n有影響<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbc9b3e51f0e493fa55a75cbb25e9bf5c37cb8d","tid":1764170,"uid":21398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:12:33.0